            <div type="a">
                <column>01</column>
                <head>An Abominable Nuisance</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The paper calls on the "town authorities" to take action against what they
                    call the "gangs of worthless lounging, vulgar niggers that congregate on the
                    corners of the streets Sabbath after Sabbath, completely blockading the
                    sidewalks, rendering it almost impossible for gentlemen and ladies to pass on
                    their way to and from church."</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
